Indeed, this is why I propose we separate these issues. Specifically, let's use this PR to land the server-chosen key ID, and then make it smaller (as needed) in a followup change. (Personally, I'm fine with one, two, or four bytes here, as I think the decryption failure case is unavoidable.) I'll file an issue for the size of the ID in a bit.

